    Class Description
    AlaCarteItem
    Stores information about an AlaCarteItem to be used in context of a menu such as its name, price, description and the type of AlaCarteItem it is.
    AlaCarteItemType
    Enumeration to indicate the type of AlaCarteItem
    AppInterface
    Interface for application to be inherited
    Customer
    Represents a customer entity inherit from Person class.
    Database
    Stores and retrieves serialized RRPSS object.
    ExpiredReservationsRemover
    Represents a TimerTask object which can be scheduled to be executed by a timer.
    Invoice
    Stores information of an order invoices in the restaurant.
    MenuApp
    Interface of the Menu App which has the option of add/remove etc.
    MenuItem
    An abstract class for AlaCarteItem and PromotionalSet used to store information about an item
    MenuMgr
    Manages the AlaCarteItem and PromotionalSet of the MenuMgr.
    Order
    Stores all important information of an order created for a customer.
    OrderApp
    Interface of the Order App which has the option of create/remove etc.
    OrderMgr
    Manages all the Order objects of the whole restaurants, basically the "manager" of RRPSS to Order objects
    Person
    A parent class for Customer and Staff class
    PromotionalSet
    Stores information about a PromotionalSet inherit fromMenuItem class to used in context of a menu.
    Reservation
    Represents a Reservation object to reserve a table.
    ReservationApp
    Interface of the ReservationApp which has the option of create/remove etc.
    ReservationMgr
    Manager of all reservations and tables.
    RRPSS
    The main application where the RRPSS works.
    SalesReport
    Manage and print restaurant sales report daily or monthly.
    Sex
    Enumeration to indicate the sex of a Person
    Staff
    Stores information about a Staff inherit fromPerson class
    StaffApp
    Interface of the Staff App which has the option of create/remove etc.
    StaffMgr
    Manages the Staff
    Table
    Represents a table object in the restaurant.
